---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | Findsera";
const description =
  "Read how Findsera handles basic analytics, affiliate links, cookies, advertising partners, and contact email.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/privacy-policy">
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-shell max-w-4xl">
      <span class="eyebrow">Privacy</span>
      <h1 class="mt-6 font-serif text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-ink-700">
        This policy explains the basic information Findsera may collect when readers browse product pages,
        use site search, click affiliate links, or contact the site.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">Last updated: May 30, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="container-shell max-w-4xl space-y-6">
      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Information Findsera collects</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          Findsera does not ask readers to create accounts. The site may process ordinary technical data such as
          page views, browser type, approximate location, referring pages, device information, and basic interaction
          events so the site can understand what content is useful and fix broken experiences.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Analytics and cookies</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          Findsera uses analytics tools, including Google Analytics, to understand aggregate site usage. These tools
          may use cookies or similar technologies to measure pages visited, traffic sources, and general engagement.
          You can control cookies through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Affiliate links and advertising</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          Some links on Findsera are affiliate links, including Amazon links. If you click a qualifying link and make
          a purchase, Findsera may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Advertising partners, including
          Google, may use cookies or similar technologies to serve and measure ads if ads are enabled on the site.
          Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits to this site or
          other websites. Google's advertising cookies enable Google and its partners to serve ads based on those
          visits. You can manage personalized advertising in
          <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" class="font-semibold text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-500">
            Google Ads Settings
          </a>
          or learn about broader opt-out choices at
          <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/" class="font-semibold text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-500">
            aboutads.info
          </a>.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Contact email</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          If you email Findsera, the site receives the information you choose to send, such as your email address,
          page URL, product name, and message. That information is used to respond to the request, correct site
          content, or handle partnership questions.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Third-party sites</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          Findsera links to retailers, brands, and other third-party websites. Those sites have their own privacy
          practices and terms. Review their policies before sharing personal information or completing a purchase.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-black/6 bg-white p-6 shadow-card">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink-900">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-ink-700">
          For privacy questions or correction requests, email
          <a href="mailto:hello@findsera.com" class="font-semibold text-accent-600 hover:text-accent-500">
            hello@findsera.com
          </a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
